Loki,is,a,service,that,adds,locations,to,websites,When,a,website,visitor,visits,a,site,with,Loki,the,visitor,s,exact,location,can,be,identified,enabling,location,based,advertisements,local,businesses,and,local,social,media,The,Loki,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Loki,s,functionality,into,websites,The,API,calls,for,locations,of,visitors,and,IP,addresses,to,accurately,access,Loki,s,location,functions